{"tid":2410814,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"碧基以粗言穢語大叫：要控球在腳啊！X你","createTime":"2021-02-17T02:20:06.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-17T10:53:24.000Z","uid":1426,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"4efae11c7afefbb020fc9d4306e6e84ad74879d8","tid":2410814,"uid":1426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T02:20:06.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports】巴塞隆拿於周二歐聯主場以1:4慘負巴黎聖日耳門，碧基與隊友基斯文在場上的對罵內容曝光。<br />\n周二歐聯16強首回合，巴塞隆拿主場1:4不敵巴黎聖日耳門，而早在38分鐘就有崩潰的現象。38分鐘，基斯文回防輸掉角球後，中堅碧基（Gerard Pique）跟他爆發罵戰。<br />\n<br />\n碧基以粗言穢語大叫：「要控球在腳啊！X你！要控好皮球！」基斯文不甘示弱：「冷靜！不要大呼小叫！X你！」碧基鬧道：「他媽的基斯文！我們備受壓力，已經頂了整整5分鐘！」基斯文回敬：「不要呼喝我！我也在受罪！」最後朗格利介入才令兩人停止罵戰。<br />\n<br />\n巴黎聖日耳門今仗控制場上主動權，令碧基為首的防線疲於奔命，結果下半場再失3球，巴塞主場這樣大敗，處於被淘汰的邊緣。"},{"pid":"e6ed9aa72aa2537584e80260e549050878f95fd8","tid":2410814,"uid":307927,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T02:21:23.000Z","msg":"不要呼喝我！我也在受罪！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f2d49dfb92a730996730581fd7447abd58de78c","tid":2410814,"uid":200882,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T02:30:18.000Z","msg":"佢地啲中文又講得幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11174ff03294fe6b07aa114b9c6be1a8c978c5c1","tid":2410814,"uid":46587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T02:35:06.000Z","msg":"X=?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60aba9370fdd999cb4d933dc26479b3d95a3d7ab","tid":2410814,"uid":126219,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T02:38:05.000Z","msg":"給我控，往死裡控，控球怎能小了我"},{"pid":"df2699fec271f0b936c37ade4e2c9f499ca2a102","tid":2410814,"uid":17619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T02:38:06.000Z","msg":"往死裡打"},{"pid":"bfba3409f51a1c41ac7f471b5aa9aff98f5a4b79","tid":2410814,"uid":310469,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy"